00:20:39.489 --> 00:20:42.909 position:50% align:center
I'm sick of playing nice.
I wanna torch this stupid world!

00:20:42.992 --> 00:20:45.328 position:50% align:center
Get in my way and I'll kill you!

00:20:45.412 --> 00:20:46.996 position:50% align:center
