00:21:08.893 --> 00:21:10.979 position:50% align:center
That's what Fire Soldiers
and knights do.

00:21:11.062 --> 00:21:12.564 position:50% align:center
It's what heroes do.

00:21:12.647 --> 00:21:14.065 position:50% align:center
[FIRST PILLAR]
